  "3194310": {
    "name": "Pixel Dungeon VR: Prologue",
    "steam_appid": 3194310,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194310/extras/b575fc8c488ae1387396892ab020d1f3.avif?t=1749123427\" width=616 height=346 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>融合Dungeons of Eternity和Ancient Dungeon的核心玩法，升级Battle Talent的战斗爽感，多人联机合作地牢游戏像素地牢带你进入VR圈的Minecraft，探索未知的世界！</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>购买完整版游戏Pixel Dungeon VR，解锁更多地图与内容，与朋友一起踏上更多激动人心的地下城之旅！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💥 BOSS战，每场都超燃</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>骷髅王</strong>挥动巨斧，小骷髅一窝蜂围攻你；<strong>幽魂领主</strong>爆炸攻击，发射子弹追你跑！<strong>堕天使</strong>秒变形，化身巨眼怪物狂扫死亡镭射；<strong>时间之神</strong>变身巨人震碎地面，所有人直接掉入第二战场，战斗升级炸翻天！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194310/extras/6c786f456494b46224b6ffdd96523310.poster.avif?t=1749123427\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194310/extras/6c786f456494b46224b6ffdd96523310.webm?t=1749123427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194310/extras/6c786f456494b46224b6ffdd96523310.mp4?t=1749123427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⚔️ 丰富武器库，管饱不重样</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >飞<strong>美队盾牌</strong>砰砰打敌人！<strong>金刚狼爪</strong>刷刷刷抓怪！变<strong>鹰眼神射手，长弓连发</strong>嗖嗖全中！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发现宝箱？</strong> 快打开，稀有武器等你拿！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还可以<strong>升级武器</strong>！两星变三星？伤害又翻倍！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194310/extras/acec53cb10f643caf0fe06a2b64443c9.poster.avif?t=1749123427\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194310/extras/acec53cb10f643caf0fe06a2b64443c9.webm?t=1749123427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194310/extras/acec53cb10f643caf0fe06a2b64443c9.mp4?t=1749123427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👑超多英雄造型，自定义你的形象！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>冷酷猎魔人、霸气黑骑士、神秘鸟人</strong>...角色超多随便选！还能<strong>解锁神秘皮肤奖励</strong>——谁说地牢里不能穿得潮一点？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194310/extras/b496b5d888eff3fa9caa8e074de3c44c.poster.avif?t=1749123427\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194310/extras/b496b5d888eff3fa9caa8e074de3c44c.webm?t=1749123427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194310/extras/b496b5d888eff3fa9caa8e074de3c44c.mp4?t=1749123427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>✨免费也好玩</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>地图随机变</strong>，每一关都超新鲜！<strong>像Minecraft一样自由探索</strong>，暗门机关到处藏，宝箱、苹果等你来发现！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>和朋友一起玩！</strong> 一起打怪超带劲，在地牢玩猜拳？搞怪笑翻天！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>丰富场景</strong>：禁忌图书馆、阴森监牢、远古遗迹...场景多到逛不完!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>点亮天赋树</strong>：无论是专精敏捷闪避策略、还是伤害爆表攻击，你都有选择！学习不同的技能，让你每次战斗都有全新体验！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>怪物大乱斗</strong>：呆萌史莱姆蹦蹦跳，恐怖骷髅头咔咔笑，打怪根本停不下来!小心涌出的蜘蛛，快打掉它的巢穴！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194310/extras/3fab8c74865efec560eab3066c651e32.poster.avif?t=1749123427\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194310/extras/3fab8c74865efec560eab3066c651e32.webm?t=1749123427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194310/extras/3fab8c74865efec560eab3066c651e32.mp4?t=1749123427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
